text: Natalia Voskobovich (born 25 October 1993) is a Belarusian footballer who plays as a goalkeeper and has appeared for the Belarus women's national team. ==Career== Voskobovich has been capped for the Belarus national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * , part 1 * , part 2 * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian women's footballers Category:Belarus women's international footballers Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:FC Minsk (women) players
